# Authors

## Original implementation

juanmacasado

- Original research and device investigation.
- Wide AMOLED Gamut mode mapping.
- HAL modification and flashable module implementation.
- Testing and validation on the OnePlus 7 (guacamoleb).
- Documentation and ROM integration patch.

GitHub: https://github.com/juanmacasado

## Upstream project

The LiveDisplay HAL modified by this project originates from
The LineageOS Project and is distributed under the Apache License 2.0.

## Immediate build source

The specific prebuilt bytes patched by this project were extracted from an
Infinity-X (Android 16, guacamoleb) build. See `NOTICE` and `SOURCE.md` for
details. Infinity-X is not affiliated with this project.
